### EduPortal API - Student Payment Plans Controller
### Student payment plan management endpoints
### Base URL: http://localhost:5000
### Requires Authentication

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000/api/student-payment-plans
@contentType = application/json
@token = {{$dotenv TOKEN}}

### ===========================================
### GET ALL PAYMENT PLANS - (Admin, Muhasebe, Kayitci)
### ===========================================
GET {{baseUrl}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ===========================================
### GET PAYMENT PLAN BY ID
### ===========================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ===========================================
### GET PAYMENT PLANS BY STUDENT
### ===========================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/student/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ===========================================
### GET ACTIVE PAYMENT PLAN BY STUDENT
### ===========================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/student/1/active
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ===========================================
### GET PAYMENT PLAN STATISTICS - (Admin, Muhasebe)
### ===========================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/statistics
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ===========================================
### GET OVERDUE PAYMENT PLANS - (Admin, Muhasebe)
### ===========================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/overdue
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ===========================================
### CREATE PAYMENT PLAN - (Admin, Muhasebe, Kayitci)
### ===========================================
POST {{baseUrl}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "studentId": 1,
  "totalAmount": 50000.00,
  "numberOfInstallments": 10,
  "startDate": "2024-09-01",
  "notes": "2024-2025 eğitim ödemesi"
}

### ===========================================
### CANCEL PAYMENT PLAN - (Admin, Muhasebe)
### ===========================================
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/1/cancel
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

"Öğrenci kaydı iptal edildi"

### ===========================================
### COMPLETE PAYMENT PLAN - (Admin, Muhasebe)
### ===========================================
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/1/complete
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

